title: 12/01/2020 - Best of The Herd

description:
-The Seahawks have improved enough to be considered a title contender

-Give yourself credit, you were right about the Bucs

-Carson Wentz isn't completely to blame for the Eagles struggles

-Aggressive teams like the Rams and Seahawks win in the NFL

-The Herd Hierarchy: Colin's top ten teams in the NFL


Guest: Andrew Whitworth, Rams Left Tackle
